The paper deals with a phase retrieval algorithm that is robust against outliers. This problem is relevant in several areas of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), numerical analysis (cs.NA), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
